commit.message:
Add universal wheel

Allows calling:
python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel
twine upload dist/*

to relase both source and binary (universal wheel) distribution of the package.

Remove phonenumbers dependency

I could not found any reference to phonenumbers in the code.

Use Xenial Build Environment

Python 3.7 is only available there

pypy versions need to be defined in a weird way.
See https://travis-ci.community/t/pypy-2-7-on-xenial/889
Add tests for all supported Python versions
Add Python 3.7 support

Drop Python 3.3 support

Flake8 won't run with Python 3.3

Fix isort

The new isort version changed the sorting
Import sort fixes to please isort
Fix DeprecationWarning: cgi.escape is deprecated, use html.escape instead in Python 3.7
Update docs, closes #59
